<h2><a href="./viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=47&amp;start=15">Proposal to include &lt;di&gt;-like element</a></h2>
<!-- NOTE: remove the style="display: none" when you want to have the forum description on the topic body --><div style="display: none !important;">Do you think the HTML spec should do something differently? You can discuss spec feedback here, but you should send it to the WHATWG mailing list or file a bug in the W3C bugzilla for it to be considered.<br /></div>

